---
layout: base.njk
title: Contact
description: Get in touch with Rebekah Monson for speaking, consulting, or collaboration.
permalink: /contact/
---

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 6rem;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-info">
        <p class="section-label">Get in touch</p>
        <h2>Let's talk <span class="emoji-hover" data-animation="wave">&#x1F44B;</span></h2>
        <p>
          Whether you're looking for a speaker, a strategic consultant, or just want to
          connect &mdash; I'd love to hear from you. Fill out the form or find me on one
          of the platforms below.
        </p>

        <div class="office-hours">
          <h3><span class="emoji-hover" data-animation="bounce">&#x2615;</span> Office Hours</h3>
          <p>
            Are you a woman, person of color, or LGBTQ person in journalism or technology?
            I do weekly digital office hours on Monday afternoons for project feedback
            and career planning. Let's connect!
          </p>
          <a href="{{ site.calendly }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--primary" style="font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem;">
            Book office hours
          </a>
        </div>

        <ul class="social-links">
          <li><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/{{ site.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/{{ site.github }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <form class="contact-form" action="{{ site.formEndpoint }}" method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New message from rebekahmonson.com">
        <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false">
        <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="{{ site.url }}/contact/?thanks=true">

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="topic">What's this about?</label>
          <select id="topic" name="topic">
            <option value="speaking">Speaking engagement</option>
            <option value="consulting">Consulting project</option>
            <option value="collaboration">Collaboration</option>
            <option value="media">Media / Press</option>
            <option value="other">Something else</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" required placeholder="Tell me about what you're working on..."></textarea>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">
          Send message <span class="emoji-hover" data-animation="bounce">&#x1F4E8;</span>
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
